reviews.text:
Excellent stuff! Subtle delicious creamy peppermint with a pleasant texture to keep you going. I really enjoy the use of the butter, biscuit, and sugar cookie to make a well balanced cookie base for the peppermint to lay with. Great as S&amp;V But certainly does develop more over time -- the cookie comes out a bit more and the creaminess seems to get a little creamier. If you have the ingredients, definitely mix this up. &#xD;
&#xD;
Thanks for the delicious mix and inspiration!
